# 🚀 NovaByte Onboarding Repository

Welcome to NovaByte’s Engineering Onboarding System.

This repository simulates real-world engineering tasks across Backend, Frontend, and Full-Stack roles. Each engineer is assigned tasks based on their role and must fix bugs in the codebase.

---

# 🧠 How This Works

1. You are assigned a role (Backend / Frontend / Full-Stack / Python)
2. Each role has predefined **tickets (bugs)**
3. You must:

   * Fix the issue
   * Run verification scripts
   * Paste output into the onboarding agent

---

# 📁 Project Structure

```
backend/            → Node.js APIs
python_service/     → FastAPI service
frontend/           → React components
scripts/            → Verification scripts
```

---

# ⚙️ Setup Instructions

## 🔹 1. Clone the Repository

```
git clone <repo-url>
cd novabyte-onboarding
```

---

## 🔹 2. Backend Setup (Node.js)

```
cd backend
npm install
node server.js
```

Runs on: http://localhost:3000

---

## 🔹 3. Python Setup (FastAPI)

```
cd python_service
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run server:

```
python -m uvicorn app:app --reload
```

Runs on: http://localhost:8000

---

## 🔹 4. Frontend (Optional for FE role)

```
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

